methods.copyField:
Copy fields from a chunk of Kafka key or value objects to a chunk that will be published to a stream table.

:param inputChunk: (io.deephaven.chunk.ObjectChunk<java.lang.Object,io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.Values>) - the chunk containing Kafka keys or values
:param publisherChunk: (io.deephaven.chunk.WritableChunk<io.deephaven.chunk.attributes.Values>) - the output chunk for the provided field
:param sourceOffset: (int) - the source chunk offset
:param destOffset: (int) - the destination chunk offset
:param length: int
